..TEXT:
|aspro~: The smoke stings the eyes.  See the
corresponding "fummo" of the irascible in Styx, there termed
"acerbo" (^Inf.~ IX, 75).  |pelo~: The term continues the
metaphor of "velo," denoting pile, as of a woven fabric.
