|per tornar bella a colui che ti fece~: To God, who
breathes the soul into the body when it is formed (^Purg.~ XXV,
70-75).  See vss. 85-90.  The soul is created directly by God and
is His creature.  "Ti mondi" and "tornar bello" recall ^Purg.~ II,
75 and 122-23, the image of the snake shedding its old skin.
