..TEXT:
|nel cielo~: "Cielo" in this context means the
heavens, i.e., the stars and planets in their respective spheres,
which shed their influence on mortal creatures.  |nel cielo
uno~, ^e un qua gi@u la pone~: Some assign the cause to the
heavens, others to men.  |qua gi@u~: In the living, in men.
