..TEXT:
|gi@a biancheggiare~: They now approach the edge of
the cloud of smoke which had overtaken them, and the light of the
sun increases in "whiteness."  (This is not the radiance of the
angel, as some commentators choose to understand it.) Marco must
remain within the smoke and so must now turn back.  The angel is
stationed on ahead and would see Marco if he emerged from the
smoke.  |me~ = ^a me.~
